    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an AI job filtering assistant.\n\nThe user is a final year Computer Science student looking for entry level roles.\n\nOnly keep jobs that match these conditions:\n\n* Role type: Intern, Internship, Trainee, Associate, Graduate, or Junior\n* For BTech Student\n* Experience required: 0–1 years (freshers allowed)\n\nIgnore jobs requiring:\n\n* 2+ years experience\n* Senior / Lead / Principal roles\n* Manager roles\n\nFor each job listing provided, extract the following fields:\n\ncompany\nrole\nlocation\nexperience_required\nskills\napply_link\nsource\n\nThen classify the job level as one of:\nintern, junior, trainee, associate, graduate, or reject.\n\nIf the job is NOT suitable for a fresher, mark:\n\"reject\": true\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON in this format:\n\n{\n\"company\": \"\",\n\"role\": \"\",\n\"location\": \"\",\n\"experience_required\": \"\",\n\"skills\": [],\n\"apply_link\": \"\",\n\"source\": \"\",\n\"level\": \"\",\n\"reject\": false\n}\n\n\nTitle: {{ $json.title }}\n\nCompany: {{$json.company}}\n\nSource: {{ $json.source }}\n\nURL: {{ $json.url }}\n\nLocation: {{ $json.location }}\n",
        "batching": {}
      },
