    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Automated Job Aggregator for Freshers\n\nThis workflow automatically collects job listings from multiple job sources and filters them for entry-level candidates.\n\n### What this workflow does\n1. Fetch job listings from multiple APIs\n2. Convert and normalize job data\n3. Merge all job sources into a single dataset\n4. Use AI to filter relevant roles\n5. Store the final results in Google Sheets\n\n### Target roles\n• Internship  \n• Trainee  \n• Associate  \n• Junior roles  \n• 0–1 years experience\n\n### Purpose\nHelp a final year student automatically discover relevant jobs daily without manually searching job boards.\n",
        "height": 576,
        "width": 416
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -1696,
        -432
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "b32d544b-9b6e-4e2a-8c85-7088b4bb4642",
